    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Oshi Clan, Level 10+</p><p>Your performances leave your viewers especially energetic, making their bodies tired without their minds realizing it. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Creatures under the effects of your Genjutsu, Oshi Clan Hijutsu, or that are Charmed by you become your Fans for the duration that those effects persist. Fans gain a +2 bonus to their AC and all saving throws against effects from creatures hostile to you.</p></li><li><p>Once per turn, when a Fan would fail a saving throw caused by an Oshi Hijutsu by 5 or more, you can choose to make them gain 1 rank of Exhaustion, up to a maximum of 5.</p></li><li><p>Once per turn, when you would inflict at least 1 rank of Charmed on a creature, you can inflict an equal amount of ranks of Dazzled.</p></li><li><p>Twice per rest, as a bonus action on your turn, you can select any number of creatures under the effects of one or more of your Genjutsu. Those creatures must make a Charisma saving throw, gaining 1 rank of Concussed for each Genjutsu they are under on a failure.</p></li></ul>",
